  <summary><div class=3D"accordion__toggle bold"><div>What makes Casper mat=
tresses different?</div><span class=3D"circle-chevron group-hover:colors gr=
oup-expanded:colors group-expanded:rotate"><svg role=3D"presentation" focus=
