      </svg></span>
    </div>
  </summary>

  <div class=3D"accordion__content"><div class=3D"prose"><p>Casper mattress=
es are developed by a team of sleep obsessed engineers and designers, plus =
a Certified Professional Ergonomist=E2=80=93 true experts dedicated to deli=
vering the sleep you deserve. We have two rules: everything we design must =
be tested and must help sleep. Let Casper help you choose the perfect new m=
attress for your home. Over the past 11 years we have taken valuable feedba=
ck from sleepers like you to design the best products for a great night=E2=
=80=99s rest. </p><p>Our Zoned Support=E2=84=A2 system provides optimal spi=
nal alignment without sacrificing comfort =E2=80=94 giving you the choice b=
etween the comfy =E2=80=9Con the bed=E2=80=9D feel of the Dream and a cozy =
=E2=80=9Cin the bed=E2=80=9D experience with the Snow. The Dream Max and Sn=
ow Max have also earned endorsements from American Chiropractic Association=
 so you can rest assured, no matter your sleep needs, Casper=E2=80=99s got =
you covered. </p><p>We pioneered the 100 night trial and easy return proces=
s, making it simple to upgrade your old mattress with confidence. Prefer to=
 try before you buy? Visit one of our <a href=3D"https://stores.casper.com/=
" target=3D"_blank" title=3D"store locator">sleep shops</a> where you can b=
ook a nap and try our products in person. Whether you stop by a store, give=
 us a call, or check our online mattress store our sleep specialists are he=
re to help build the bedroom of your dreams!</p></div></div>
</details>
<details class=3D" accordion  group" aria-expanded=3D"false" is=3D"accordio=
n-disclosure">
  <summary><div class=3D"accordion__toggle bold"><div>What is a mattress in=
