lass=3D"circle-chevron group-hover:colors group-expanded:colors group-expan=
ded:rotate"><svg role=3D"presentation" focusable=3D"false" width=3D"8" heig=
ht=3D"6" class=3D"icon icon-chevron-bottom-small" viewBox=3D"0 0 8 6">
        <path d=3D"m1 1.5 3 3 3-3" fill=3D"none" stroke=3D"currentColor" st=
roke-width=3D"1.5"></path>
      </svg></span>
    </div>
  </summary>

  <div class=3D"accordion__content"><div class=3D"prose"><p>A mattress in a=
 box is a mattress that=E2=80=99s compressed in an air-sealed bag and rolle=
d tight so that it can fit into a box that=E2=80=99s easier to maneuver tha=
n a traditional mattress. This innovation gives you the freedom to explore =
our mattress collection, compare choices, and order the best mattress for y=
our needs online, all delivered straight to your door. <br><br>When you rec=
eive the mattress, all you=E2=80=99ll need to do is pull it out of its pack=
aging, lay it flat on your bed frame or floor, and let it expand.<br><br>Fo=
am and hybrid mattresses can be slept on almost right away but may take up =
to 48 hours to expand fully. Our Snow mattresses are primarily made with me=
mory foam and can take up to 72 hours to expand fully.</p></div></div>
</details>
<details class=3D" accordion  group" aria-expanded=3D"false" is=3D"accordio=
n-disclosure">
