roke-width=3D"1.5"></path>
      </svg></span>
    </div>
  </summary>

  <div class=3D"accordion__content"><div class=3D"prose"><p>Every Casper ma=
ttress is engineered for both comfort and durability, our premium foams (an=
d innerspring coils inside our Hybrid mattresses) provide lasting support f=
or a full decade=E2=80=94our <a href=3D"https://casper.com/pages/warranty" =
target=3D"_blank" title=3D"Warranty">warranty</a> backs it up.</p></div></d=
iv>
